{"tid":1163411,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"西環騎硬鴕 - 陳也","createTime":"2019-05-20T12:16:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T12:16:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9a3cf2debe650bbe30cd19e0e910c698cad3d79c","tid":1163411,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T12:16:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20190520/20682320\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190520%2F20682320&d=RsYziF%2F%2FwXRI7aJQ3s5lGZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=634690f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190520%2F20682320&h=e2405a8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20190520/20682320</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n西環騎硬鴕 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190520/large/e8813a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190520%2Flarge%2Fe8813a.jpg&h=7afd7698&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗傳話，西環叫香港人要有四個相信。點止四個，係柒個！<br />\n<br />\n一，相信西環會拆天。<br />\n<br />\n二，相信林鄭月鴕，日日鴕，年年鴕，陀衰家。<br />\n<br />\n三，相信西環行埋，露骨玩變態，騎住鴕，上佢！<br />\n<br />\n四，相信鴕至叻，一發功，贏晒50萬人上街後「被腳痛」，斷纜落台收返23條的老懵董。又跑贏強推831袋住先方案，但臨尾等埋發叔，冥冥中甩轆的689。相信鴕，好快修例成為第13個生肖。<br />\n<br />\n五，相信立法會秘書，一票都冇，憑什麼阻撓民選議員開會？立法會秘書處，相信已經唔當香港人係老闆，出糧畀佢的，西環都唔相信是西環。<br />\n<br />\n六，相信在香港賣樓賣股、更心急將美國資產調走的建制派和小老闆，唱國歌時比80歲阿婆更需要輪椅，走資走唔切，個個都腳軟啊。<br />\n<br />\n七，相信七百萬人有同一個夢，逃犯條例講明第一個被引渡的人叫做梁振英，市民幫周浩鼎諗埋，無論佢逃去天堂邊忽都屎！  <br />\n<br />\n陳也 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n哈佛大學英文？ (古德明)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n在屋頂上寫字 (楊靜)"}]}